<section>
<h2>Homework Tasks (Q1–Q6)</h2>

<!-- Q1 -->
<div class="question-block">
<div class="question-header">
  <span class="question-pts">18 pts</span>
  <span class="question-title">Q1 — Value Iteration</span>
</div>
<div class="question-body">
<p>Implement <code>ValueIterationAgent</code> — an offline planner that computes optimal values using the Bellman equation:</p>
<pre><code>V_{k+1}(s) = max_a  Σ_{s'} T(s,a,s') · [R(s,a,s') + γ · V_k(s')]</code></pre>
<p>Implement three methods in <code>students/value_iteration_agents.py</code>:</p>
<ol>
  <li><code>run_value_iteration()</code> — the main loop (batch updates!)</li>
  <li><code>compute_q_value_from_values(state, action)</code> — Q from V</li>
  <li><code>compute_action_from_values(state)</code> — best action from V</li>
</ol>
<div class="card warning">
  <div class="card-label red">Important</div>
